												<DIV>"When you zone the charmed pet doesn't follow you ... does the suspended pet still vanish?"</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Pretty sure any suspended pet will "poof" if you zone and it does not actually have to be zoning across a zone line either.&nbsp; Last night I had a pet suspended and we inzone evac'ed (which causes a zone like effect), when we touched down my suspended pet was no more.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>- Bril</DIV>
																		
